cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper deals with image analysis and machine learning techniques for sex prediction from periocular images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of multiple sensors and spectra suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of machine learning techniques indicates that the paper may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
